          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "If you‚Äôve been on the internet long enough, you‚Äôll have used Snopes. In the late 90s and early 2000s, it was the go-to site for debunking viral email chain letters, and then their reincarnated form on Facebook. But, even as misinformation has surged on the old interwebs, Snopes has slowly faded from relevance.",
            "type": "text",
